OL,3,CThe whiskey maker keeping cows happy
OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,FCows on a Welsh farm are being fed on
OL,7,Fa diet of malted barley left over from
OL,8,Fmaking whiskey in an effort to help
OL,9,Fthe environment.
OL,11,FThe Aber Falls Distillery in
OL,12,FAbergwyngregyn is just 500 yards away
OL,13,Ffrom Pentre Aber Farm, which is
OL,14,Fplaying a key role in reducing
OL,15,Femissions from the site.
OL,17,FFarmer Will Davies' 400 cattle tuck
OL,18,Finto four tons of the barley every
OL,19,Fday, left over from the whiskey stills
OL,20,Fat the distillery.
