OL,3,CThe whiskey maker keeping cows happy
OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,FThe arrangement is part of the
OL,7,Fdistillery's wider efforts to become
OL,8,Fmore eco-friendly, with the water used
OL,9,Fto make the whiskey being pumped from
OL,10,Fa borehole and the visitor centre cafe
OL,11,Fusing an array of solar panels.
OL,13,F"It's a win-win for both of us. We get
OL,14,Frid of a waste product that we'd
OL,15,Fotherwise have to pay to have taken
OL,16,Faway and the farmer gets free feed for
OL,17,Fhis cows," Head Distiller Sam Forster
OL,18,Fsaid of the arrangement.
