OL,3,CThe whiskey maker keeping cows happy
OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,FHe added: "Almost all our barley comes
OL,7,Ffrom Pembrokeshire but if any farmers
OL,8,Fcloser to home would like to grow a
OL,9,Fcrop we'd be happy to hear from them."
OL,11,FFarmer Edward Davies said with the
OL,12,Ffeed coming from just down the road,
OL,13,Fthe food miles are short.
OL,15,FThe trailer comes to the distillery
OL,16,Fonce a day to pick up a the feed for
OL,17,Fthe cows.
OL,19,FBut does it contain any alcohol?
