OL,3,CThe whiskey maker keeping cows happy
OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,F"A lot of people think it tastes like
OL,7,Fwhiskey and it makes the cows drunk
OL,8,Fbut it doesn't," he said.
OL,10,FHe joked: "I don't think you get the
OL,11,Ftaste of whiskey through the milk,"
OL,12,Fadding "I think we'd soon hear from
OL,13,Fthe South Caernarfon Creamery if we
OL,14,Fdid."
OL,16,FThe efforts have been praised by
OL,17,FAshley Rogers, chief executive of the
OL,18,FNorth Wales Business Council, which
OL,19,Fruns the Net Zero North Wales Network.
