OL,3,CThe whiskey maker keeping cows happy
OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,F"What Aber Falls and Pentre Aber Farm
OL,7,Fare doing here, using the resources we
OL,8,Fhave within our own businesses and
OL,9,Fworking with local partners to make
OL,10,Fthe best use of them, is an amazing
OL,11,Fexample of the circular economy in
OL,12,Faction," he said.
OL,14,FMr Rogers added: "This working
OL,15,Ftogether and sharing ideas is at the
OL,16,Fheart of how North Wales will get to
OL,17,FNet Zero.
