OL,4,Con the road to net zero
OL,6,F"Aber Falls is a real trailblazer, not
OL,7,Fjust in terms of making wonderful
OL,8,FWelsh whiskey but also in the
OL,9,Finnovative ways they are using to
OL,10,Foperate in such an environmentally
OL,11,Ffriendly way.
OL,13,F"You can't get much greener than
OL,14,Ffeeding the malted barley to cows just
OL,15,F500 yards away."
